{"id":232906031,"title":"學鋼琴必經之路 - Clementi sonatina","content":"相信各位彈鋼琴的朋友，都必定經過\nClementi Sonatina op36. no.1\n這首曲的洗禮吧，也是跟有彈鋼琴不論初中高級的朋友都是非首有共鳴的一首曲。\n\n最近太空閒時去買了一套錄音器材，打算把整套Opus36都錄了，當做是示範影片，希望對大家有幫助。\n\nSonatina Op. 36, No. 1(Complete)\nhttps://youtu.be/bcR0naJzSTg\nSonatina Op. 36, No. 2(Complete)\nhttps://youtu.be/31Iv3ndAVz0\nSonatina Op. 36, No. 3(Complete)\nhttps://youtu.be/hu4Rs9ErmnY\n\n未來有空時我應該會製作一些實用而又很少人會教的鋼琴技巧，有在學鋼琴的朋友記得繼續留意囉😉","excerpt":"相信各位彈鋼琴的朋友，都必定經過，Clementi Sonatina op36. no.1，這首曲的洗禮吧，也是跟有彈鋼琴不論初中高級的朋友都是非首有共鳴的一首曲。最近太空閒時去買了一套錄音器材，打算","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":false,"pinned":false,"forumId":"885f988a-c7bf-4e24-a308-2560f8da8a0e","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2020-01-17T06:24:31.045Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-17T06:24:31.045Z","commentCount":1,"likeCount":7,"tags":["HIDE_THUMBNAIL"],"topics":["鋼琴","古典音樂"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":true,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"音樂","forumAlias":"music","school":"LeoTsui","department":"leotsui123","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":false,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":7}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":false,"withVideos":false,"media":[],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"3a065543-5a31-442a-953a-88fa472f8dc9","url":"https://youtu.be/bcR0naJzSTg","normalizedUrl":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bcR0naJzSTg","thumbnail":"https://img.youtube.com/vi/bcR0naJzSTg/hqdefault.jpg","type":"video/youtube","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2020-01-17T06:24:31.045Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-17T06:24:31.045Z"},{"id":"13091c4f-68e0-4e62-a1fc-6691ce7d859a","url":"https://youtu.be/31Iv3ndAVz0","normalizedUrl":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=31Iv3ndAVz0","thumbnail":"https://img.youtube.com/vi/31Iv3ndAVz0/hqdefault.jpg","type":"video/youtube","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2020-01-17T06:24:31.045Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-17T06:24:31